+### WP11: End-to-End Hardening
+
+**Mode:** final sequential integration package.
+
+**Goal:** Verify that Projects + Workflows work while Sessions remains stable.
+
+Tasks:
+
+- Run typecheck and unit tests.
+- Add integration tests for Projects routes and Workflow APIs.
+- Browser-test Sessions tab regression.
+- Browser-test Projects tab creation and workflow status.
+- Verify debug CLI output for Workflow Runs.
+- Verify no third-party workflow framework dependency was added.
+- Verify destructive cleanup requires explicit confirmation.
+
+Acceptance criteria:
+
+- Sessions tab can still create/select/send/archive sessions as before.
+- Projects tab can create/select a Project.
+- A `standard-project` Workflow Run can be started and inspected.
+- Workflow trace explains state transitions.
+- User feedback can approve/request changes/discard.
