+## 10. Testing Strategy
+
+### Unit Tests
+
+- Workflow definition validation.
+- Workflow store persistence.
+- Trace event ordering.
+- Runner transitions and retries.
+- Project API serialization.
+
+### Integration Tests
+
+- Start Workflow Run.
+- Resume waiting run.
+- Discard run.
+- Link Workflow Run to Pibo Session.
+- Fetch Workflow Run and trace through Chat Web API.
+
+### Browser Checks
+
+- Sessions tab still works.
+- Projects tab opens.
+- Projects tab visually matches Sessions and includes the green Personal Chat row.
+- Project list/select works and stays on Projects routes.
+- Creating a Project does not navigate to Sessions.
+- Workflow status appears.
+- User feedback buttons work.
+
+### Manual Debug Checks
+
+```text
